T1  - THE STRUGGLE FOR EXISTENCE: MIGRATION, COMPETITION, AND HUMAN CAPITAL ACCUMULATION IN HISTORIC CHINA
AU  - Bai, Ying
Y1  - 2022/08/01
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2022/08/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/iere.12565
